table 'Deal Overview Layout'
	lineageTag: 303bf2a5-f6bc-461f-8089-3340c0451a47

	measure 'Deal Overview Value' = ```
			
			  VAR _Metric = SELECTEDVALUE('Deal Overview Layout'[ ])
			  RETURN
			  SWITCH(
			      _Metric,
			      "Current Principal Balance", FORMAT(SUM('Deal Overview'[Current Principal Balance]), "$#,0"),
			      "Initial Advance", FORMAT(SUM('Deal Overview'[Initial Advance ]), "$#,0"),
			      "Commitment", FORMAT(SUM('Deal Overview'[Original Commitment]), "$#,0"),
			      "Target Gross IRR (%)", FORMAT(SUM('Deal Overview'[Target Gross IRR (%)]), "0.00") & "%",
			      "Target Gross Cash Multiple", FORMAT(SUM('Deal Overview'[Target Gross Cash Multiple]), "0.00") & "x",
			      "Target Levered IRR (%)", FORMAT(SUM('Deal Overview'[Target Levered IRR (%)]), "0.00") & "%",
			      "Target Levered Cash Multiple", FORMAT(SUM('Deal Overview'[Target Levered Cash Multiple]), "0.00") & "x",
			      "Loan Type", SELECTEDVALUE('Deal Overview'[Loan Type 2]),
			      "Note Rate (Floor)", SELECTEDVALUE('Deal Overview'[Note Rate (Floor)]),
			      "Term", SELECTEDVALUE('Deal Overview'[Term]),
			      "Extension Options", SELECTEDVALUE('Deal Overview'[Extension Options]),
			      "Asset Type", SELECTEDVALUE('Deal Overview'[Asset Type Primary]),
			      "Property Size", FORMAT(SUM(Collateral[Property Size]), "#,0"),
			      "Guaranty", SELECTEDVALUE('Deal Overview'[Guaranty]),
			      BLANK()
			  )
			```
		lineageTag: 7fc126ec-7b50-4f96-a866-2cd835864788

